snippet.textDisplay: I'm 49, a father, husband, self-taught drummer, guitarist and music lover. I originally wrote this young lady off as a wannabe musician. Then it hit me - her vocal control is unbelievable. As a few have said here... she's not whispering. Her vocals require extreme control. Her emotion cannot be taught. I'm not perfect and I prejudged Ms. Eilish. For this I'm sorry. Happy to say I'm officially a genuine fan. PS- The father in me wants to tell her to go wash the green out of her hair. LOL. But really I think she's a great musician.
snippet.textOriginal: I'm 49, a father, husband, self-taught drummer, guitarist and music lover. I originally wrote this young lady off as a wannabe musician.
